Packages 
Package Description
com.ushahidi.java.sdk
The Implementation of Ushahidi public API
com.ushahidi.java.sdk.api
This package contains all the model classes representing the various resources available through the Ushahidi API such as reports,category, location, country,etc.
com.ushahidi.java.sdk.api.tasks
This package contains the classes that invoke the Ushahidi API calls and returns the model classes representing the various resources available through the API invokation.
com.ushahidi.java.sdk.net
This package contains classes for communicating with the Ushahidi API over HTTP or HTTPS depending the protocol supplied.
